\s1 Jesus is Lord of the Sabbath\f + \fr 2:23 \ft Between verses 22 and 23 all of John chapter 5 takes place—that chapter revolves around the second Passover of His public ministry, in 28 \sc ad\sc* A year and a half have passed since His baptism.\f*
