\v 50 Tossing off \w his|strong="G4314"\w* \w cloak|strong="G2440"\w*,\f + \fr 10:50 \ft Now why did he abandon his cloak? He expected to be healed—being able to see he could easily find it (and who else would want a beggar's cloak?).\f* \w he|strong="G1161"\w* got \w up|strong="G2064"\w* \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w went|strong="G2064"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*.
